_sText:
So I made this map in 20 minutes and people on my server loved it.
I wasn't going to release it but people said a should.

I made this map in tribute to my server (NS Gungame) NS as a whole is a bunch of different servers but my server is in the spotlight lately. I named it Noskill because that's the name of the clan.

The idea of the map is really... Carnage! 64 spawn points but designed for a 14 man server.

It looks very basic but I spent time making as many entrances and ways to go as possible.
Hopefully the map won't be discredited for just plain being 'too small'.


So enjoy.

PS: Works nice on DM :)
